Intel Core i5-10210U Processor: The Intel Core i5-10210U is a power-efficient quad-core SoC for notebooks based on the Comet Lake (CML-U) generation and was announced in August 2019. Compared to the similar Whiskey Lake processors (e.g. Core i5-8665U), the only difference is support for higher memory speeds (up to LPDDR4-2933 vs DDR4-2400) and two additional cores in the top model (not in this i5). The processor cores are clocked between 1.6 and 4.2 GHz (all 4 cores 3.9 GHz max).
14 inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) display: 14.0" 1920 x 1080 FHD Display. Engineered for long-lasting performance.

Woov Accessory Bundle: Bundled with a wireless mouse that offers smooth and precise navigation.
